Wrapper class for the 4.6 version of GNUPLOT. :param input_xvg_path_dict: Dict where keys are mutations (str) and

values are paths (str) to xvg rmsd files.
Parameters:

  • properties (dic) – output_plotscript_path (str): Path to the output GNUPLOT script file. gnuplot_path (str): Path to the GNUPLOT executable binary.
